                <h1>Dom Pedro II</h1>

                <figure style="align-items: center;">
                    <img style="height: 250px;" alt="retrato de dom pedro segundo criança" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Pedro_II_of_Brazil_-_Brady-Handy.jpg/245px-Pedro_II_of_Brazil_-_Brady-Handy.jpg">
                    <figcaption class="caption">Retrato de Dom Pedro II (1887). </figcaption>
